data.description: Welcome to Brandywine! This charming 2nd floor condo shows like a dream. This open concept unit has LVP floors throughout the living area, freshly painted rooms and updated lighting fixtures throughout. Open concept kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and cozy dining area. Fantastic screened in porch with ample storage. Two absolutely spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with updated features. Plus a NEW HVAC and ROOF! Scenic views and walking area plus a neighborhood pool and grassy play area with grills! Minutes from uptown and Plaza Midwood. Call this property home today!
